Name: The Rainbow World
About the game: A kingdom fallen, a prince exiled. Restore her glory, his journey begins. Features: Exploration Explore a big and interconnected world, gaining new abilities to take on new areas! Combat Mix of Top-down shooter and Hack-and-slash combat, with multiple skills for different enemies. Air Combat Jump into your airship to explore and fight in the air. Platforming Use combat abilities to traverse the terrain. Chill in Town Discover towns and other locales through your journey.
